WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en-US

00:00:22.932 --> 00:00:25.132
Did the bailiff lock us in here?

00:00:25.132 --> 00:00:27.980
What do they think we are, crooks?

00:02:24.996 --> 00:02:26.356
So why do you vote not guilty?

00:02:54.860 --> 00:02:56.570
Yeah, so what's bothering you?

00:02:56.574 --> 00:02:58.314
Why don't you think he's guilty?

00:02:58.314 --> 00:02:59.934
 I'd like to hear it. 

00:03:43.558 --> 00:03:46.060
Only an ignorant man can believe that.

00:03:46.060 --> 00:03:48.079
Just because this kid is a different color than you...

00:04:19.374 --> 00:04:21.411
Yeah, she said that she couldn't sleep,

00:04:21.414 --> 00:04:23.514
She was in bed and happened to be

00:04:23.514 --> 00:04:25.303
looking across the way at their

00:04:25.303 --> 00:04:27.036
apartment when she saw him stab his father.

00:05:31.024 --> 00:05:33.152
I've lived in a slum all my life.

00:05:33.154 --> 00:05:34.911
I used to play in a backyard

00:05:34.911 --> 00:05:36.433
that was filled with garbage.

00:05:36.434 --> 00:05:38.020
Maybe it still smells on me!

00:05:53.094 --> 00:05:54.854
No, that's not right.

00:05:54.854 --> 00:05:56.765
Only the woman claimed to have seen it.

00:06:01.709 --> 00:06:03.644
The old man only heard the body fall.

00:06:03.644 --> 00:06:05.284
 He didn't see the stabbing. 

00:06:05.284 --> 00:06:07.132
Then he said he saw the kid running

00:06:07.132 --> 00:06:09.121
down the stairs and out of the house.

00:06:09.124 --> 00:06:10.373
So he called the police.

00:06:34.207 --> 00:06:35.839
That's true, but the woman was far away,

00:06:36.344 --> 00:06:38.404
 wasn't she? About 60 feet.

00:06:38.404 --> 00:06:40.684
Why are you rubbing your nose like that?

00:06:40.684 --> 00:06:43.159
I want to know why are you rubbing your nose.

00:06:57.424 --> 00:06:59.099
Your eyeglasses makes those deep

00:06:59.099 --> 00:07:01.414
impressions on the sides of your nose.

00:07:01.414 --> 00:07:03.604
I never noticed that before.

00:07:03.604 --> 00:07:04.980
They must be annoying.

00:07:04.980 --> 00:07:07.044
The woman who testified that she

00:07:07.110 --> 00:07:08.838
saw the killing had the same

00:07:08.838 --> 00:07:10.803
 marks on the sides of her nose. 

00:07:14.954 --> 00:07:17.488
This woman was about fourty-five years old,

00:07:17.494 --> 00:07:19.662
 but she tried to look thirty-five. 

00:07:19.662 --> 00:07:22.743
Did you notice that? All that makeup,

00:07:22.743 --> 00:07:24.192
 her hair dyed,

00:07:24.194 --> 00:07:26.861
the brand new clothes and no eyeglasses? 

00:07:39.694 --> 00:07:41.619
 Could those marks be made by anything  

00:07:41.619 --> 00:07:43.153
 other than eye glasses? 

00:07:43.154 --> 00:07:44.318
I don't think so.

00:07:44.318 --> 00:07:46.362
And no one wears glasses to bed.

